      <div class="author-content">
        <div class="author-kicker">About the Author</div>
        <h3 class="author-name">Birkley<strong>Grunewald</strong></h3>
        <p class="author-role">Writer - Researcher - Correspondent</p>
        <p class="author-bio">
          These papers represent an ongoing attempt to think clearly about politics, economy, and the structures that
          shape how people live. Written across years of study and travel, they range from formal academic arguments to
          shorter reflections on questions that resist easy answers.
        </p>
        <p class="author-bio">
          The work sits alongside photography, travel writing, and short fiction, each form asking a different kind of
          attention from the same underlying preoccupations.
